ooui-outline-control-move-down: Tool tip for a button that moves items in a list down one place
ooui-outline-control-move-up: Tool tip for a button that moves items in a list up one place
ooui-outline-control-remove:
Tool tip for a button that removes items from a list.
{{Identical|Remove item}}
ooui-toolbar-more:
Label for the toolbar group that contains a list of all other available tools.
{{Identical|More}}
ooui-dialog-message-default-accept:
The default label for the accept button of a confirmation dialog.
{{Identical|OK}}
ooui-dialog-message-default-reject:
The default label for the reject button of a confirmation dialog.
{{Identical|Cancel}}
ooui-dialog-action-dismiss: Label for action dialog dismiss button, visible when listing errors
ooui-dialog-action-retry: Label for action dialog try again button, visible when listing recoverable errors
